{"tid":1301929,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"放榜又訓唔著可以入來","createTime":"2019-07-09T18:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T19:01:58.000Z","uid":214482,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8b4166afc0c7c60c4c3c81ae6a1e12e4309a2c39","tid":1301929,"uid":214482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:38:52.000Z","msg":"一大早就放榜，好多手足都訓唔著。係正常既反應，因為以前我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後成班都係班group吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早少少同同學去食早餐，查定交通方式、campus 位置。<br />\n定啲嚟！唔好亂！唔好急！<br />\n<br />\n出門口之前睇吓有無帶漏嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）錢（報名費、留名費、食飯錢、車錢）<br />\n2）八達通（坐車、用汽水機）<br />\n3）雨傘<br />\n4）外套（等interview 個冷氣好涷）<br />\n5）高中成績表&amp;副本備用<br />\n6）身份證&amp;副本備用<br />\n7）conditional offer （如有）<br />\n8）證件相<br />\n9）文具（好多form 要寫）<br />\n10）電話<br />\n11）隨叉<br />\n12）手提電腦（非必備）<br />\n<br />\n休閒衣著即可，T-shirt 牛仔褲 波鞋（周圍走唔好玩命）<br />\n拎完沙紙，睇吓有無同路人一齊去，互相照應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成績合乎預期既，去相應院校報到。恭喜恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成績差啲既，唔好緊張，睇吓去邊間報FD/HD/ASSO，<br />\n注意！唔好報非主流/非正規註冊既大專院校！留意課程資歷架構同認可，唔好亂交錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到咩咩學校、咩咩學院，唔係本地營運既課程（所謂同英國、澳洲合辦/聯辦課程）打醒十二分精神！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好可能無認受性，提防受騙！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未諗定繼唔繼續讀既，唔好見人讀你又讀，到頭來中途quit 浪費錢同時間。自己諗清楚先好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家定啲嚟、唔好緊張，夜晚食餐好既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝各位 順順利利  學運亨通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed14c7ec4355e03dcf42ab2e950ea39221a84ea4","tid":1301929,"uid":214482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T19:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3zJBpZ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3zJBpZ9.png&h=a0f83e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報讀非本地高等及專業教育課程前，注意該課程是否經已辦理註冊或豁免註冊及相應的資歷架構級別。切勿一次繳交全部學費。要索取並保留學費收據。如有疑問，請到教育局網站查詢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://applications.edb.gov.hk/ncr/ncr.aspx?langno=2&amp;searchtype=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapplications.edb.gov.hk%2Fncr%2Fncr.aspx%3Flangno%3D2%26searchtype%3D3&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBF9PyQTEnBXXUT3Ba6PvfAw%3D&h=847ad973\" target=\"_blank\">https://applications.edb.gov.hk/ncr/ncr.aspx?langno=2&amp;searchtype=3</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局關心您。"}]}